When menu pop-up has no space to place, pop-up location changes to wrong position.

Sorry, but this fix introduces bug #8757

I fixed this bug in master with and 0c1a742da7fe1f6214f01b5d58a914aab20c5b75 branch_4_0_x with f0f2b972b1987b563f5baf1266093ea8e9a0d9b4
Problem: I expected and tested that _placementTarget is a widget that contains the getBounds method. But in your case _placementTarget is an object with left and top because it will open as a context menu.
Solution: Now it covers the 2 possible values for _placementTarget: widget and object (with top and left)
